Type: Package
Package: openalexSnowball
Title: Snowball searches for OpenAlex using the openalexPro pipeline
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Rainer M Krug
Maintainer: Rainer M Krug <Rainer@krugs.de>
Description: Perform snowball searches on the OpenAlex citation graph using
    openalexPro's on-disk processing pipeline and store results in Parquet.
